{"tw": {"3417490": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "With Eyes Closed - Season 2", "steam_appid": 3417490, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >緊接著第一季結尾的驚險懸念，第二季將為你的故事開啟全新篇章。本季帶來全新的角色關系，以及出人意表的劇情反轉，就是要讓你從頭到尾都沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>沒玩過第一季嗎？不用擔心！本遊戲內含簡單的前情提要，新玩家也能快速上手，暢快享受精彩刺激的故事。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>**主要特色**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 分支故事線：</strong>你的選擇將決定故事的走向，揭開全新的發展和結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/c411626f4bc9de5f768fc445acc9d9f7.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/c411626f4bc9de5f768fc445acc9d9f7.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/c411626f4bc9de5f768fc445acc9d9f7.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 迷人的角色：</strong>與七位各有千秋的女性角色相遇，每位角色都能和你發展出一段獨特的關系，帶來截然不同的劇情體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b37c8c946bc6fe034667b8d51855f66d.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b37c8c946bc6fe034667b8d51855f66d.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b37c8c946bc6fe034667b8d51855f66d.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>升級版視覺效果</strong>：享受 2K QHD 畫質、60 FPS 畫面，以及超過 100 段精心製作的動畫。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>**全新角色：**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>哈珀</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/03876e804b758f8bb60a97cd6ee6cfae.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身為露娜的神秘夥伴，哈珀充滿自信，個性大膽機靈。你能否卸下她的心防、揭開她的秘密？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>芭芭拉</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/7da7e584047cf2efc1494ae7fa787692.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾經擔任記者的芭芭拉，如今試圖採訪一位權勢滔天的黑幫成員。你願意協助她完成這項大膽的任務嗎？而她又會如何回報你呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong> 奧莉維亞：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/bf62e9d9616752d5774bd8d5a83cb33d.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是位身材火辣的性感熟女，平時就愛和搭檔一起做瑜伽。你準備好幫助她維持完美身材了嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong> 梅琳達：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/cab728f49905a18e21a9b2c8cf116b9d.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是位經驗豐富的掮客，專門為傭兵牽線兼做情報交易。要贏得她的青睞絕非易事，但有什麼能比成熟幹練的美女更吸引人的呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>**回歸角色：**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong> 凱特：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/2982dc712eb9deb58e0110ccbf86a436.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是一位紅髮美人，值得信賴，總是樂於提供協助。你很難找到比她更棒的朋友了，尤其是考慮到她那傲人的魔鬼身材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>伊娃</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/8ab08045f74dadf45124bf92005a12ce.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這位金髮醫生有著動人心魄的湛藍雙眼。面對這位作風獨立的冰山美人，你能揭開她所隱藏的秘密嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>露娜</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/518fdb29f5fe3082de3b3fffc350ac8a.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是一位落難的年輕女子，而你是唯一能幫助她的人。但她又會選擇如何回報你呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快加入 With Eyes Closed 的玩家社群，與同好們一起探索精彩刺激的全新篇章！</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/151a80c7119a5202aa7fc65cd9072dd2.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >緊接著第一季結尾的驚險懸念，第二季將為你的故事開啟全新篇章。本季帶來全新的角色關系，以及出人意表的劇情反轉，就是要讓你從頭到尾都沉浸其中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>沒玩過第一季嗎？不用擔心！本遊戲內含簡單的前情提要，新玩家也能快速上手，暢快享受精彩刺激的故事。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>**主要特色**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>- 分支故事線：</strong>你的選擇將決定故事的走向，揭開全新的發展和結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/sto