"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Ubuntu 12.04+ or Kernel 3.x+ based distributions<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> 2.0 GHz Core 2 Duo<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> OpenGL 2.0 or DirectX 9.0c compatible<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 7 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 2 季"}}}}, "us": {"3417490": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "With Eyes Closed - Season 2", "steam_appid": 3417490, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b17249c02314a9053398332f1e743f0a.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b17249c02314a9053398332f1e743f0a.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Season 2 picks up where the thrilling first season left off, following your story beyond the life-or-death cliffhangers. Dive deeper into the narrative with new relationships and unexpected twists that will captivate you from the start.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>If you missed the first season, no worries! The game includes a brief recap, allowing newcomers to quickly catch up and enjoy the exciting storyline.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**KEY FEATURES**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/e79fba421ab4cb3c5d4c9a8de7b59979.mp4?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Branching Storyline:</strong> Your decisions continue to shape the narrative, revealing new possibilities and consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/5917bae3b2a59c8e3a6117d5961144be.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/5917bae3b2a59c8e3a6117d5961144be.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Engaging Characters:</strong> Meet seven diverse female characters, each offering unique relationships and experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/af4e78bf4b10921fa993bceaaec131f6.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/af4e78bf4b10921fa993bceaaec131f6.webm?t=1776323321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Enhanced Visuals:</strong> Experience 2k QHD, 60 fps, and over 100 meticulously crafted animations.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**New Characters:**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Harper:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/03876e804b758f8bb60a97cd6ee6cfae.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious associate of Luna, Harper is confident and a bit cheeky. Will you be able to break through her defenses and uncover her secrets?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Barbara:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/7da7e584047cf2efc1494ae7fa787692.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a journalist, now seeking an interview with one of the most powerful mobsters. Will you assist her on this daring mission, and how might she repay you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Olivia:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/bf62e9d9616752d5774bd8d5a83cb33d.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curvaceous MILF who loves to do yoga with a partner. Are you ready to help her stay in perfect shape?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Melinda:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/cab728f49905a18e21a9b2c8cf116b9d.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A seasoned broker dealing in jobs for mercenaries and trading in information. Winning her favor won't be easy, but what could be more enticing than an experienced and sophisticated woman?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**Returning Characters:**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Kate:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/2982dc712eb9deb58e0110ccbf86a436.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A redheaded beauty who's trustworthy and always ready to help. You could hardly wish for a better friend, especially one with such captivating curves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Eva:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/8ab08045f74dadf45124bf92005a12ce.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A blonde doctor with striking blue eyes. Can you discover what's hidden behind her self-sufficient and icy facade?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <strong>Luna:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/518fdb29f5fe3082de3b3fffc350ac8a.avif?t=1776323321\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young lady in distress, with you as her only savior. But how will she choose to reward you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the community of players already enchanted by With Eyes Closed and explore the next exciting chapter for your character!</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3417490/extras/b17249c02314a9053398332f1e743f0a.poster.avif?t=1776323321\" width=780 height=439 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app